            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3598Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of six episodes/events, showing: first, the three Arabs swimming in the water; second,  one man being eaten by a crocodile;
                    third, the two others standing on a rock above the water;  fourth, one man riding a camel to the monastery, which is depicted in the background; fifth,
                    the other man bringing his sheep's wool and sixth, the camel brought by the Arab eating from a tree.</p>
